article.description: — Collin Welp posted 15 points as UC Irvine topped Cal Poly 68-49 on Friday.
article.headline: Welp scores 15 to lift UC Irvine over Cal Poly 68-49
article.linkText: Welp scores 15 to lift UC Irvine over Cal Poly 68-49
article.story: IRVINE, Calif. -- — Collin Welp posted 15 points as UC Irvine topped Cal Poly 68-49 on Friday. JC Butler had 14 points for UC Irvine (7-4, 3-0 Big West Conference), which earned its fifth consecutive victory. Brad Greene added 12 points. Tuukka Jaakkola had three blocks for the Mustangs (2-9, 0-5), who have now lost seven straight games. Colby Rogers, the Mustangs’ second leading scorer entering the contest at 10 points per game, shot only 20% in the game (2 of 10). ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
